<anchor id="adxl__store_8h_1adxl_store"/> <simplesect kind="par"><title>Detailed Description </title><para>Measurement raw data will be stored in FRAM. FRAM space needs to be allocated and reserved. Every second acceleration data will be measured and stored with a data rate of 4400 samples per second. Maximal 15 times acceleration data shall be measured, that means after 15 seconds the complete measurement cycle is finished and the RMS data will be send via LTE.</para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="remark"><para>This source code is confidential and proprietary information of AXO Track GmbH, Berlin. You may not disclose, copy, or distribute this source code or any part thereof without the explicit permission of AXO Track GmbH, Berlin. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
